description:
Main Responsibilities:
-Closely work with Product Manager for product development;
-Take product feature ownership and manage full life cycle of the requirement;
-Produce and maintain product backlog and participate in or drive sprint planning where appropriate;
-Produce business and use cases where necessary to support product requirements;
-Produce high quality business analysis artifacts in a timely manner, including user story, software requirement specification, functional specification;
-Collaborate with UX & Visual designers for wireframe and visual assets;
-Driving grooming meetings with implementation teams, and play an active role to clarify requirements and decision making to ensure implementation;
-Communicate with customer/support and provide customer support where necessary;

Requirements:
-Excellent English skills;
-Must have strong analytical skills and problem solving skills;
-Must possess excellent written and interpersonal communication skills and be able to effectively communicate across all levels of the organization;
-Experience in requirement management, including requirements gathering, analysis, and specification documentation;
-Ability to assume intellectual ownership and possess strong attention to details and commitment to delivering quality product;
-Ability to work effectively with cross-functional teams and synthesize cross-functional input in a team/collaborative environment;
-Ability to learn and adapt quickly;
-Experience in agile software development and web product design is preferred.

1，统招二本以上学历，
2，良好的C/C++基础;
3、熟悉Linux操作系统或者Windows操作系统原理、熟悉基本的算法和数据结构;
4、责任感强，工作认真负责

扎实的基本功，熟练掌握 Python;
熟练掌握 Flask, Tornado 中至少一种 Web Framework;
 熟练掌握 PostgreSQL, MySQL 中至少一种 RDBMS, 熟悉 Redis 等常用 NoSQL;
具备良好的分析问题、解决问题的能力，喜欢尝试新技术，乐于分享，优秀的团队协作精神;
具有职业操守，维护公司利益。

加分项

精通 PostgreSQL; 熟悉 golang 并有实际项目经验; 
对自然语言处理或深度学习有研究或感兴趣;
Github 有项目超过 100 star，或给大型项目贡献过代码; 写技术博客（或微信公众号）2 年以上，或者 50 篇以上;
熟练在 Mac OS X / Linux 上开发。

Responsibilities:
Mobile application development on Android platform.

Requirements:
- At least 3 year experience of mobile application development on Android platform;

- BS degree or above on Computer Science, Electronic Engineering or Mathematics;

- Problem solving skills and good attitude;

- Good team spirit, responsible, autonomy, open-minded.

岗位职责：
线上和线下阿里云系统及云服务的规划（包括网络规划，安全规划，容量规划等），系统的运维、优化及业务系统的自动化发布，系统及业务监控报警的规划和维护工作
    
岗位要求：
1、熟悉服务器、存储的巡检和监控; 
2、熟悉系统事件监测、通知、升级、故障隔离及解决;
3、熟悉各类虚拟化容器镜像的构建如docker等； 熟悉虚拟化调度框架的运行及维护 包括Mesos（Marathon）， Kubernetes等
4、熟悉系统安全加强、系统补丁程序管理，保证系统更加稳定和安全的运行; 
5、熟悉虚拟化场景下业务系统系统部署、升级扩容; 
6、熟悉VPC及网络规划，能够根据业务进行整体业务网络的划分和网络安全规划
7、掌握一门脚本语言Python或者Shell; 
8、熟悉自动化工具的使用如Ansible
9、熟悉多个阿里云产品，有多年阿里云系统运维经验优先

星垂智能 ZENO 是一家总部在西安的科技创业公司，由连续创业者们创立，创始人们曾在美国，阿联酋等地工作和创业。目前 ZENO 处于影藏模式中，已经获得来自阿联酋，加拿大和新加坡的客户。公司位于西安，并在迪拜设有分公司。
公司提供完善的福利制度和行业内 Top 5% 的薪资。我们期望新同事拥有良好的英文沟通能力，对新技术的敏锐性和对新鲜事物的好奇心。

Job Responsibilities
1. Provide full spectrum of administrative support to general manager, including but not limited to internal and external meetings scheduling, business and private reception and travel arrangements;
2. Responsible for the preparation of conference materials, conference management and preparing meeting minutes and reports;
3. Assist in preparing presentation materials and speeches for public events and media interviews;
4. Assist in arranging monthly expenses, making expense report and dealing with the reimbursement;
5. Closely work and communicate with clients and internal parties to resolve problems;
6. Perform tasks as assigned.

Job Requirements
1. Bachelor's degree or above from a well-recognized university (local & overseas);
2. 3 years of tech industry work experience, familiar with business etiquette,
3. Good command of spoken and written Chinese and English;
4. Well-organized, motivated and detail-minded
5.Basic schedule management, information processing, reimbursement management, document processing, administrative management, meeting/event support capabilities;
6. Proficiency PC knowledge in office software, excellent PowerPoint presentation skills;
7. Honest, fast learner with strong sense of responsibility.

【岗位职责】
1. 你将会在敏捷开发中迭代式的修改和还原高保真原型，以及产品的交互和后端 数据集成;
2. 参与设计人员对产品的交互以及用户体验设计，参与业务分析并对产品提出改 进反馈和调整;
3. 参与项目的代码规范制定，技术框架的选型;
4. 成为项目里前端代码的质量控制者，保证这些代码清晰优雅并能够跨浏览器和
平台保持一致性;
5. 将会和后端开发人员以及UX一起结对共同交付一个开发任务 (我们叫它用户
故事);
6. 会和其它开发人员一起共同编写一份业务代码(我们叫它结对编程);
7. ThoughtWorks是一个鼓励学习和尝试新职业体验的组织，我们希望你能够把
  你的想法和经验传播到我们全球更广泛的社区中。

【必备技能】
1. 扎实的HTML/CSS/JAVASCRIPT基础知识;
2. 对W3C规范，HTML语义化有较深刻的理解，对原生JS有熟练的掌握;
3. 对语义化HTML，CSS盒模型，渐进增强，响应式设计等有的深入理解;
4. 熟悉并掌握至少一种主流前端框架 （例如: Angular.js、React、Vue; Redux、
Ember.js ; RxJS）及开发流程;
5. 能够熟练且高标准的还原设计稿以及响应式页面;
6. 解决跨浏览器兼容性问题的经验;
7. 良好的沟通能力——你需要经常和客户沟通、对话，并且能说服他们，打破这
  些同行的怪癖和思维定势;
8. 一颗好奇心，关注行业资讯，关注主流框架及标准的更新;

【加分技能】
1. 熟悉node.js及主流开发框架 （Express.js;koa.js）;
2. SASS/LESS/PostCSS, Babel等代码预处理以及编译工具的使用;
3. 前端开发工程化项目实践 (Webpack, BDD/TDD, CI 等);
4. 了解移动端开发（react-native; weex）;
5. 良好的英文听说读写能力。

